opinions.text:
ORDER
PER CURIAM.
AND NOW, this 25th day of July, 2014, the Petition for Writ of Mandamus is DENIED. The Prothonotary is directed to strike the name of the jurist from the caption.
opinions.author: PER CURIAM.
